{"word":"H885 - בְּאֵרֹת בְּנֵי־יַעֲקַן - Bᵉʼêrôth Bᵉnêy-Yaʻăqan - be-ay-roth' be-nay' yah-a-can' - Beeroth of the children of Jaakan","slug":"H885","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בְּאֵרֹת בְּנֵי־יַעֲקַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Bᵉʼêrôth Bᵉnêy-Yaʻăqan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>be-ay-roth' be-nay' yah-a-can'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Beeroth of the children of Jaakan"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05EA; &#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05D9;&#x05BE;&#x05D9;&#x05E2;&#x05E7;&#x05DF; - b<sup>e</sup>'e&#x0302;ro&#x0302;th b<sup>e</sup>ne&#x0302;y</b>-<b>ya&#x201B;a&#x0306;qan</b> - <i>be-ay-roth' be-nay' yah-a-can'</i><p/>From the feminine plural of <a href=\"#/H875\">H875</a>, and the plural contraction of <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a>, and <a href=\"#/H3292\">H3292</a>; <i>wells of</i> (the) <i>sons of Jaakan</i>; <i>Beeroth Bene-Jaakan</i>, a place in the Desert: - Beeroth of the children of Jaakan."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1268\">H1268</a>, <a href=\"#/H1275\">H1275</a>, <a href=\"#/H1307\">H1307</a>, <a href=\"#/H3565\">H3565</a>, <a href=\"#/H5626\">H5626</a>, <a href=\"#/H874\">H874</a>, <a href=\"#/H875\">H875</a>, <a href=\"#/H876\">H876</a>, <a href=\"#/H877\">H877</a>, <a href=\"#/H878\">H878</a>, <a href=\"#/H879\">H879</a>, <a href=\"#/H880\">H880</a>, <a href=\"#/H881\">H881</a>, <a href=\"#/H882\">H882</a>, <a href=\"#/H883\">H883</a>, <a href=\"#/H884\">H884</a>, <a href=\"#/H886\">H886</a>, <a href=\"#/H953\">H953</a>"}]}